COMPOSER

hacker@hacker:~$ wget https://getcomposer.org/composer.phar
hacker@hacker:~$ mv composer.phar composer
hacker@hacker:~$ chmod +x composer 
hacker@hacker:~$ ./composer 
hacker@hacker:~$ mv composer /usr/local/bin/


refer:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YpGNQzY7bFQ

